author: Brooke Singman, Blake Burman
title: White House memos warned in run-up to pandemic of up to 2M deaths, economic devastation
description: Top White House trade adviser Peter Navarro warned in stark terms about how deadly and economically devastating the coronavirus outbreak could be, weeks before it became a full-blown pandemic.
